void ObitUVImagerIonFromInfo (  ObitUVImager *  out,
gchar *  prefix,
ObitInfoList *  inList,
ObitErr *  err
) 
 

Public: Init UVImager object from description in an ObitInfoList.

Initializes class if needed on first call.

Parameters:
out the new object.to be initialized
prefix If NonNull, string to be added to beginning of inList entry name "xxx" in the following
inList InfoList to extract object information from
  • "xxxClassType" string UVImager type, "Ion" for this class
  • "xxxUVData" prefix for uvdata member, entry with value "None" => doesn't exist
  • "xxxUVWork" prefix for uvwork member, entry with value "None" => doesn't exist
  • "xxxMosaic" prefix for mosaic member, entry with value "None" => doesn't exist
  • "xxxIonTab" prefix for ionTab member, entry with value "None" => doesn't exist
  • "xxxsnVer" olong SN table version to use, 0> add new
err ObitErr for reporting errors.
Returns:
the new object.
